<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Focal on Notes</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/tags/focal/</link><description>Recent content in Focal on Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Nov 2020 12:36:20 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.harues.com/tags/focal/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>System Level Linux DNS over TLS on Ubuntu 20.04</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/posts/system-level-linux-dns-over-tls-on-utuntu-20.04/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Nov 2020 12:36:20 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://notes.harues.com/posts/system-level-linux-dns-over-tls-on-utuntu-20.04/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="system-level-linux-dns-over-tls-on-ubuntu-2004">System Level Linux DNS over TLS on Ubuntu 20.04&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="prerequisite">Prerequisite&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>stubby&lt;/li>
&lt;li>dnsmasq&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="installation">Installation&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="stubby">stubby&lt;/h3>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo apt install stubby
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;h4 id="start-and-endable-stubby">Start and endable stubby&lt;/h4>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo systemctl enable stubby
sudo systemctl start stubby
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre></description></item><item><title>리눅스에서 한/영 전환키 사용하기</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/posts/right-alt-as-hangul/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Oct 2020 08:35:41 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://notes.harues.com/posts/right-alt-as-hangul/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="문제점">문제점&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>영문 키보드 구입&lt;/li>
&lt;li>오른쪽 Alt&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --> 키 (&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->Alt_R&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->)을 한글 키로 사용 하고 싶음.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>IBus 등에서 한/영 변환을 &lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->Alt_R&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --> 키로 등록
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>다른 프로그램에서는 잘 동작.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->Alt_R&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --> 키를 단축키로 사용하는 프로그램(Chrome)등에서는 동작이 안됨&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->Ctrl_R&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->은 Hanja 키로 매핑 시키고 싶이 않음.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item></channel></rss>